OL,5, Two secret Falklands War files related 
OL,6, to the Sir Galahad bombing could soon  
OL,7, be released, a minister has said.      
OL,9,FThe Sir Galahad, a Royal Fleet         
OL,10,FAuxiliary (RFA) ship, was sunk by the  
OL,11,FArgentinian air force on 8 June, 1982. 
OL,13,FThe ship and sister vessel Sir Tristram
OL,14,Flost 48 crew members, including 32     
OL,15,FWelsh guards, with many more injured.  
OL,17,FDeclassified documents released last   
OL,18,Fyear revealed confusion, delays and    
OL,19,Fmissed opportunities to move them to   
OL,20,Fsafety.                                
